Housing

Sources
   •   U.S. Census Building Permits API
   •   HUD public CSVs (https://www.huduser.gov/portal/datasets/hads/hads.html)
   •   Zillow Research housing metrics (https://www.zillow.com/research/data/)
# domains/housing/data_pipeline.py
from core.pipeline.base_pipeline import fetch_csv, normalize

ZILLOW_URL="https://files.zillowstatic.com/research/public/HousingValue.csv"

MAPPINGS={
  "location":"RegionName",
  "avg_home_age":"Age",
  "avg_refi_per_decade":"RefiRate",
  "avg_material_lifespan":"Lifespan"
}

def get_housing_data():
    df=fetch_csv(ZILLOW_URL)
    return normalize(df,MAPPINGS)